# Blog Images Directory

This directory contains featured images for blog posts.

## Image Requirements
- Format: WebP primary, PNG/JPEG fallback
- Size: 1200x630px for social sharing optimization
- Optimization: All images <200KB after compression
- Alt Text: Required for all images (defined in blog post frontmatter)

